name: Nana Dogu
description:
#07/07 of DOGU - White Series

Lay down, close your eyes and listen to Nana's tales.

"Once there was a Dogu with the blackest of noses, the longest of all the tail, whose bark caused the grass to grow..."

---

The White Series focuses on combining old nature pictures with the DOGUs.

This series consists of 6 DOGUs and one secret DOGU.
